abstract: Federal jury finds in favor of New York Jets receiver Brandon Marshall, who was accused of assaulting California woman outside Manhattan nightclub in 2012.
lead_paragraph: A jury in a civil trial found that a California woman failed to prove that she had been punched by Jets receiver Brandon Marshall outside a Manhattan nightclub four years ago.
